Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make an enemy of me,\NI'll make you pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vice Admiral Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Saul, who deserted\Nwith Olvia, is attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up! Preserve the books!\NWe have to pass down the history!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop them to the lake through the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be better than them being\Nburned up and gone! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul! Stop it now! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the books out of the library!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save as many books as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preserve as many sentences as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that our predecessors' words from\Nthe past several thousand years...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will reach the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to the evacuation ship while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer survive\Nif you remain on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:18.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:28.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cross this endless sea to go in search of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:34.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a global miracle no one\Nhas yet been able to find
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:39.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our hearts pounding,\Nwe'll just charge ahead as we please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:46.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,following the footprints of\Nthose who chase their dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:52.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stormy the night,\Nif we join our hearts as one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:56.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be able to make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:04.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:10.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are tears\Nwe don't want anyone to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:16.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Nif we want to achieve our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:19.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we should always look\Nstraight ahead without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:24.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:28.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:34.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nhead past everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:40.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we don't run from it,\Nwe can grasp tomorrow in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:46.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Neverything we see before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:51.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's carve it into the blank pages of our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Brand New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:04:02.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Say You Want to Live! We Are Your Friends!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Hurry up and run!\NWhat was your mom's wish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sailing the evacuation ship out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Isn't that the monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the daughter of Olvia,\Na criminal, who was in the paper before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If we let her on the ship,\Nit might cause us trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! She's only a child!\NHurry up and get her on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuation ship! Don't let\Nthat brat come on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she's a child, she's an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a target of our attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Spandine! I-Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? If we let her come on board,\Nwe'll be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be CP9! How absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Vice Admiral Saul is coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! I guess we didn't have to\Nask Olvia about his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire the cannons at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if a Buster Call is blocked by\Na former marine, now does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take pride in this attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right! You should know it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're wiping out Ohara\Nto make an example of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is for the future of the world,\Nit can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, these scholars are\Nviolating the laws, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice changes its form\Ndepending on the position you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't criticize your sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're in our way, I can't let you be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The evacuation ship got blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cannon fire! From one of the battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was from Vice Admiral Sakazuki's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna do it, we'll do it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If even a single scholar is hiding\Non that ship by some chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sacrifices made in this\Noperation will all be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to eradicate\Neven the possibility of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something "justice" would do?!\NCan you still keep your head high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to go as far as that idiot does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna run, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's abnormally strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking a scholar with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Time Capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you stay on the island!\NSail out on my raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Saul?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for me. I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's no one on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:08:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now, but you'll\Nmeet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Robin! Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're having a hard time,\Nlaugh like this, just like I taught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet the friends\Nwho're surely waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere at sea, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live together with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also the history that humans chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How thoughtless humans are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...any parting words as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tree of Knowledge... is coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute justice can\Nsometimes drive people mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to let you escape from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth will sprout\Nfrom the seed Saul protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you bear a grudge against is up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, just be happy you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live as quietly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew lines on the sea with ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just go straight on that\Nsmall boat, you'll reach land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your enemy. I'll be the first to\Ncome after you if you cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom is on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that pain makes you want to die,\Nyou're free to do that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best library in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like books?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Robin's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud, Robin! Ohara is honorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot give up the future\Nyou young ones will live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So laugh. When you're\Nhaving a hard time, just laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems stupid to laugh\Nwhen you're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet the friends\Nwho're surely waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere at sea, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no possibility of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are enough books\Nto fill the lake completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this by chance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the brat!\NThere's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you find her?! Did you capture her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir! Keeping in mind to\Nlook out for "a suspicious girl,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we found a girl on a passenger\Nship that was leaving an island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,far northeast of Ohara,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we lost her right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got the devil's luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely saw a brat escaping\Nfrom burning Ohara on a small boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go after her, but the helm\Nsuddenly got stuck as if it was frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Mr. Saul must've let her\Nescape right before he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that she can decipher Poneglyphs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although she's still small, she's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This operation will go down\Nthe drain unless we capture her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as possible--I don't care how!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,79 million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a high bounty for an eight-year-old child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that she's a\Nsurvivor of those Ohara devils
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who planned the world's annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how, but they said\Nthat she sank six Navy battleships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why her bounty is so high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Government and\NNavy Headquarters are going after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed to have inherited the\Nideology of the executed scholars.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a problem if she's left at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a child of the devil\Nwho shouldn't be allowed to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thank you for letting me work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, before lunch, you have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let her get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give me the money!\NI reported her to you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She works very hard, although she's still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get up early tomorrow\Nmorning to go purchase stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good kid, but if we're\Nwith her, we'll be in danger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, look at this bounty amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey! She isn't in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That little brat picked up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I don't have any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about you, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a wanted man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do chores, I'll feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Contact Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Robin?! Hand her over, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn jinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sin is being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nico Robin is in this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her! Hand her over to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found one...! A Poneglyph...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come inside! I've got nothing to sell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sixteen. I'll do anything.\NPlease let me be part of your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed me, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin. I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you can read Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... you exercise a Buster Call\Nright here, right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then together with Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you guys, too, will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'd be eliminated\Nby our own people's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago,\Neverything was taken away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and many people's lives were ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was caused by a single attack--Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...targeted on the friends I was finally\Nable to find, whom I can be myself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wish to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more my fate will show its fangs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a huge enemy that I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with Aokiji, as well as this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already dragged you\Ninto my troubles twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues forever, even though\Nyou guys're good-natured...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll eventually feel that I'm a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll betray me\None day and abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm most afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That indeed is a sound argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. No one is stupid enough\Nto think that having you isn't a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that symbol, you damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That logo indicates the unity\Nof over 170 member countries
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spanning the four seas and the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you now realize how completely\Npowerless you guys are to fight against it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how huge of an organization\Nthis woman has been pursued by?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now understand well the\Nidentity of Robin's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot through that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new weapon,\Na huge slingshot... named Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good look at its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack... Firebird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They've gone and done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they understand what it\Nmeans to attack the flag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates declared war\Nagainst the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?! Don't think\Nthat you'll be able to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after making the entire world your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't heard you say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To live...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be allowed\Nto live in this world, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence itself is a huge crime, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was something I dared not wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever let me wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If... it's really okay for me\Nto utter my wish for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...! I love you guys, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:03.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:06.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:11.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:15.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll become No. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll aim for freedom in wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a faint light\Nshowing us the road to tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:23.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,an era created by risking everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We always try our best, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to achieve glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:29.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the time--don't be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:31.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll surely win the future\Ntogether with friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:34.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we start running faster\Ntowards the vast world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:38.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take off with unknown powers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:41.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't fear, and we don't waver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nin the end we'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:48.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:52.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:57.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:59.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:01.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start running towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:09.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I swore that I'd\Ngather a crew and become a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like the pirate who protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just like he protected me\Nthat time, I'll protect you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.43,0:23:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already one of us, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.14,0:23:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rescue you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jump Towards the Falls! Luffy's Feelings!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
